<HEADLINE>
<P>
DEAL OF THE WEEK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Jet Vacations, a subsidiary of Air France, is offering a winter package in 
Madrid from Jan. 3 to March 31. Prices start at $879 and include round-trip air 
fare (Monday through Thursday) from LAX, six nights accommodations with 
continental breakfast, airport transfers, hotel taxes and service charges and a 
half-day tour of Madrid. There is a $25 surcharge for Friday, Saturday and 
Sunday travel in either direction. There are no blackout dates. Rates are based 
on double occupancy and availability. For information and reservations, call 
(800) JET-0999.Free for the Asking 
</P>
<P>
 Get on the trail of the scenic West this winter on the now-complete 
Continental Divide Snowmobile Trail, running 370 miles from Lander, Wyo., to 
West Yellowstone, Mont. The 30-mile stretch of the Grand Teton National Park 
that completes the trail will open on an experimental basis this winter, from 
about January through March, depending on conditions. The trail traverses open 
meadows and crosses Yellowstone National Park. A free map is available from the 
Wyoming Snowmobile Program, 2301 Central Ave., Cheyenne, Wyo. 82002; (307) 
777-7550. 
</P>
<P>
 This Week's Holidays 
</P>
