<TEXT>
<P>
 Spice 1, "Amerikkka's Nightmare," (***) Jive. The most alarming revelation 
derived from this bright young rapper's fourth album is that nothing appears to 
be getting better in the Hayward 'hood he's chronicled for the past seven 
years. "Amerikkka" finds the youth still as uncompromising as the tough streets 
he comes from, but even more bitter and, as "Strap on the Side" indicates, 
well-armed. Dennis Hunt 
</P>
