<DOCNO> LA122594-0138 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 111270 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 25, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
