<P>
 Birdonthewire, who won five races and nearly earned an Eclipse Award last 
year, got his first victory of 1994 Saturday at Calder Race Course in Miami. 
</P>
<P>
 Birdonthewire, ridden by Craig Perret, won by 5 1/4 lengths in the $100,000 
Kenny Noe Jr.Handicap, covering seven furlongs in 1:23 3/5. 
</P>
<P>
