<HEADLINE>
<P>
ABORTIONS SHOW DECLINE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Women are getting fewer abortions and mostly seeking them in the first 
trimester of their pregnancies, federal health officials said Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 The number of legal abortions reported by the 50 states and Washington D.C., 
was 1,359,145 in 1992, the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
