<DOCID> 111431 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 25, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Page 61; Calendar Desk 
</P>
